entries.title_d: Patrol for pirates in the Corellia System. When you complete this mission, return to Sergeant Rhea in Coronet for your next assignment.
entries.title: Corellia System: Patrol Corellia Trade Route X143
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: <\#pcontrast1Pirate wing detected.  They are moving to attack!\#pcontrast3>
entries.quest_patrol_d: When you reach a patrol waypoint you will receive a new one to your next location. Follow each of the patrol waypoints until you reach the end of your patrol.  This is the first of four special assignments given to you by Sergeant Rhea. When you complete this mission, return to Sergeant Rhea in Coronet for your next assignment.  After you complete these four special assignments, Sergeant Rhea will train you in a new Pilot skill.
